{"lemma":"ذَلِيلَةٍ","slug":"ذَلِيلَةٍ","root":"ذ.ل.ل","root_slug":"ذ-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ل-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13975"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"servile"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"despicable, very contemptible"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wormy"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb ذَلَّ (ḏalla)."},"ipa":["/ða.liːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13975","headword_ar":"ذَلِيلٌ","root":"*l","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Low, base, vile, abject, mean, paltry, contemptible, despicable, ignominious, inglorious, lowered, brought low, abased, humbled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K;) applied to a man; (T, S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ul~aAnN","text_ar":"ذُلَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, as a sing.; (Ibn- 'Abbád, K:) or this latter is a pl. of the former, (T,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*il~aA='u","text_ar":"اَذِلَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*il~apN","text_ar":"اَذِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ilaAlN","text_ar":"ذِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Gentle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"merciful."},{"kind":"text","text":"Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*il~apK EalaY Almuw^ominiyna A^aEiz~apK","text_ar":"اَذِلَّةٍ عَلَى المُوْمِنِينَ اَعِزَّةٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AlkaAfiryna","text_ar":"عَلَى الكَافِرينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [v. 59], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Gentle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"merciful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the believers, rough in behaviour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the unbelievers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T.) ―         -b3-  Also applied to a road, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Made even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smooth, and easy to be travelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to walk or ride upon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; being applied to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is fem. as well as masc.] ; (M;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aluwlN","text_ar":"ذَلُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) pl. of the latter, (T,) or of the former, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ululN","text_ar":"ذُلُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, M:) and [in like manner] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu*al~alN","text_ar":"مُذَلَّلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beaten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trodden, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to walk or ride upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T:) [in like manner also] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aluwlN","text_ar":"ذَلُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to land or ground &c. [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to be travelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to walk or ride upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (As, M voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarabuwtN","text_ar":"تَرَبُوتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a wall, and to a house, or chamber; (T;) and [so] applied to a mountain: (S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dk","text_ar":"دك"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low and thin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a wall: (Mgh:) and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"short,"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a spear. (T.) ―         -b5-  You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aliylN","text_ar":"ذَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ul~N","text_ar":"ذُلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Exceeding lowness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baseness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abasing, lowness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baseness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; i. e.,] using the latter word as an intensive epithet; or as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu*il~N","text_ar":"مُذِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","Zj","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}